org.hypergraphdb.algorithms

Class HGBreadthFirstTraversal

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hypergraphdb.algorithms.HGBreadthFirstTraversal
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Iterator<Pair<HGHandle,HGHandle>>, HGTraversal

    public class HGBreadthFirstTraversal
extends java.lang.Object
implements HGTraversal

    Implements a breadth-first search of a graph. As a reminder, breadth-first will visit all atoms in an adjacency list before exploring their adjacent atoms in turn.
